<main class="main">
    <div class="intro">
        <div class="intro__inner">
            <div class="intro__logo">
                <img class="intro__logo--logo" src="images/icons/intro/solin.svg" alt="#">
            </div>
            <h1 class="intro__title">@mentalsolin</h1>
            <p class="intro__desc">Я начинающий фронтендер, изучаю c++. Люблю minecraft и делать ресурс-паки для него. Иногда дизайню сайты, ценю нестандартные решения в дизайне. Обрабатываю фотографии в фотошопе. Когда никто не видит настраиваю серваки, и изучаю линукс.</p>
            <ul class="intro__social">
                <li class="intro__social--item">
                    <img class="intro__social--item-icon" src="images/icons/intro/twitter.svg" alt="#">
                    <a class="intro__social--item-link" href="{{ links.social.twitter }}"></a>
                </li>
                <li class="intro__social--item">
                    <img class="intro__social--item-icon" src="images/icons/intro/github.svg" alt="#">
                    <a class="intro__social--item-link" href="{{ links.social.github }}"></a>
                </li>
                <li class="intro__social--item">
                    <img class="intro__social--item-icon" src="images/icons/intro/telegram.svg" alt="#">
                    <a class="intro__social--item-link" href="{{ links.social.telegram }}"></a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="intro__arrow">
            <img class="intro__arrow--animation" src="images/icons/intro/arrow_down.svg" alt="#">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="harticles">
        <div class="harticles__header">
            <h2 class="harticles__header--title">Мои статьи</h2>
            <div class="harticles__header--more">
                <img class="harticles__header--more--icon" src="images/icons/articles/more.svg" alt="#">
                <a class="harticles__header--more--link" href="articles.html"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-swiper">
            <div class="swiper projectSwiper">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper" id="swiperInner">
                    {%- for article in collections.article | reverse -%}
                    <div class="swiper-slide">
                        <article class="harticles__article">
                            <img class="harticles__article--image" src="{{ article.url + "images/preview.jpg" }}" alt="#">
                            <h3 class="harticles__article--title">{{ article.data.title }}</h3>
                            <p class="harticles__article--desc">{{ article.data.preview }}</p>
                            <a class="harticles__article--link" href="{{ article.url }}"></a>
                        </article>
                    </div>
                    {%- endfor -%}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="/scripts/modules/swiper.js"></script>
        <div class="harticle__footer">
            <img class="harticle__footer--icon" src="images/icons/articles/double_arrow_left.svg" alt="#">
            <p class="harticle__footer--slogan">Просто свайпните</p>
            <img class="harticle__footer--icon" src="images/icons/articles/double_arrow_right.svg" alt="#">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hprojects">
        <h2 class="hprojects__title">Мои проекты</h2>
        <div class="hprojects__list">
            <div class="hprojects__list--item">
                <h3 class="hprojects__list--item-title">Minecraft</h3>
                <p class="hprojects__list--item-desc">Ресурс-паки</p>
                <img class="hprojects__list--item-icon" src="images/icons/projects/arrow_right.svg" alt="#">
                <a class="hprojects__list--item-link" href="projects.html"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="hprojects__list--item">
                <h3 class="hprojects__list--item-title">Websites</h3>
                <p class="hprojects__list--item-desc">Сайты</p>
                <img class="hprojects__list--item-icon" src="images/icons/projects/arrow_right.svg" alt="#">
                <a class="hprojects__list--item-link" href="projects.html"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
